en_7365195_0	The body of the treasurer attached to the Embassy of Saudi Arabia in Sri Lanka has been discovered in a swimming pool in Bambalapitiya.
en_7365195_1	Police Media Spokesperson, SSP Ajith Rohana said that the incident was reported at 03:30 on Sunday evening.
en_7365195_2	He added that an investigation is underway to determine the cause of death.
